#: ../../S/STFW.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Usenet] Common abbreviation for \"Search The Fucking Web\", a suggestion "
"that what you're asking for is a query better handled by a search engine "
"than a human being. Usage is common and exactly parallel to both senses of "
":ref:`RTFM`\\. A politer equivalent is :ref:`GIYF`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Usenet] 「Search The Fucking "
"Web(そのクソWebを検索しろ)」のよくある略。あなたが尋ねていることは、人間よりも検索エンジンに扱わせたほうがよい問い合わせだ、という示唆。用法は\\"
" :ref:`RTFM`\\ の両方の語義とまったく同様で、一般的である。より丁寧な等価表現は\\ :ref:`GIYF`\\ 。"
